                 :producesProduct :Ammonium ,
                                  :Glucose ,
                                  :Phosphate ,
                                  :Sulphate ;
                 :isDefinedBy "Hydrolysis of biodegradable particulate organics into soluble biodegradable substrates that can be used in downstream anaerobic conversion processes." .


